➜内蒙古诗人王武（晓雨）：诗五首
http://www.sohu.com/a/438429226_100115135	37465
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201215/066d5ee13e4c45be8cd73bb53a8f6557.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝•赞精准扶贫（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong> 文/晓雨</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">中央政策暖民心，对症开方药效真。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">合力攻坚效果显，小康路上抖精神。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201215/39fbfae344644cdbb3e23adfd7273643.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七律•游龙门水都感怀（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/晓雨</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">碧水桥边几度寻，花香四溢伴霞临。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">飞珠浅玉白虹起，赏瀑观溪美梦存。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">歌漫长亭听醉客，雨滋高树洗浮尘。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">茐茐郁郁如蝶舞，天下龙腾纸上云。</p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
