<p class="ql-align-center">(一)</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一场梦幻好斑斓</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">斑斓得犹如一场熊熊大火</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>疯狂地灼伤了你</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>灼伤了你自己那一双忠实的臂膀</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">两行诗一样的热泪</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在吞噬苍穹的大火里灼热地滚烫</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>泪光里</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>有你的迷茫</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还有着你自己啊</p>
