<p class="ql-align-center">黎明前</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还有一片黑暗</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>你的脚步</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>还是静静地徘徊</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">徘徊在那一段</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">模煳了岁月的路上</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>因为你自己坚信</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>这一片被虚荣心熏黑了的尘世里</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还存留有着</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一片干净的天地</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>那就是你执着者</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>心里那宁静的诗行和远方</strong></p>
